d from the Pending Approval Listing (common queue) to the To Approve Listing (supervisor’s personal approval queue)**, where it becomes part of that supervisor’s dedicated approval workload.        \n\nThis **claiming and movement from Pending Approval Listing to To Approve Listing** is the required supervisory/quality-control step that must occur before the transfer can progress to final approval or completion.\n\n### Sources\n[1] SBI_Journey from Order Placement till Settlement_V10_SBI_CCV13.pdf  \n[2] 360ONE_Journey from Order Placement till Settlement_V11_CCV13_Part 1.pdf  \n[3] 360ONE_Journey from Order Placement till Settlement_V11_CCV13_Part 4.pdf  \n[4] HSBC_Journey from Order Placement till Settlement_V11_CCV10_Part 2.pdf  \n[5] SBI_Journey of trade capture_V10_CCV11.pdf  \n[6] SBI International_Journey of RM from Customer Meeting to Closure of Action Items_V10.pdf	\N	{"v2_workflow":true,"mode":"balanced","model":"gpt-5.1","seed_node_names":["To Approve Listing","Pending Approval Listing","Approver","supervisor","supervisor’s personal approval queue","Approval Date & Time"],"seed_node_ids":["dataentity:pending_approval_listing","report:performance_projection","datastore:supervisor_s_personal_approval_queue","dataentity:to_approve_listing","dataentity:approver","dataentity:supervisor","datastore:pending_approval_listing","system:approver","datastore:to_approve_listing","dataentity:approval_date_time"],"expanded_nodes":28,"expanded_edges":882,"kg_guided_queries":["[Focused Response Directive]\\n\\nPlease follow these instructions when answering:\\n• Answer ONLY the specific question asked - be precise and direct\\n• Include ONLY information that is immediately relevant to this specific question\\n• Exclude tangential details, background context, or loosely related information\\n• Be concise while remaining comprehensive on the core topic\\n• Prioritize clarity and relevance over exhaustive coverage\\n\\nUser's Question: What step is required by a supervisor o